{"tid":2002614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"老父涉強姦親女近10年, 女兒突拒絕再出庭, 老父無罪釋放","createTime":"2020-05-05T09:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T02:29:56.000Z","uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"0c05d6c9528da593a4a7a7357b7f50d28885213c","tid":2002614,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"老父涉性侵親女近10年 上訴得直原須重審 惟事主拒再出庭控方終撤控<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<br />\n現年63歲的父親，被指自女兒4歲起不斷非禮及強姦她，惡行持續10年，直至女兒14歲時買刀放床邊自衞才終止。涉案父親早前在高等法院經審訊後，被裁定一項非禮及三項企圖強姦罪成，判監12年。他早前指原審法官誤導陪審團，不服定罪提出上訴，及後獲裁定上訴得直，案件發還重審。惟控方今日透露，事主拒絕再次出庭作供，控方只能要求不提證供起訴。法官最終撤銷被告所有控罪，被告無罪釋放....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全文link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200505/HJ7JOGONUO5YFDNA5R7RXK6YLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200505%2FHJ7JOGONUO5YFDNA5R7RXK6YLY%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=a1db05be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200505%2FHJ7JOGONUO5YFDNA5R7RXK6YLY%2F&h=8c33e327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200505/HJ7JOGONUO5YFDNA5R7RXK6YLY/</a>"},{"pid":"278254e74eec7500441e9d57d8ab8036caffad89","tid":2002614,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:42:32.000Z","msg":"好難怪<br />\n女兒再作供=勾起自己痛苦回憶...."},{"pid":"a927bd3e68684d6c55448d0005a1f43d6e97a889","tid":2002614,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fff1092a8944600210bb0972e645a03a177246","tid":2002614,"uid":1231,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實每一次提起都係揭返起佢既傷疤"},{"pid":"1918ccbf1354cd32a5dbfa4963bec661d2ba400